      <title>南非股市的上涨取决于超出预期的盈利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/south-african-stocks-rally-hinges-on-beating-earnings-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非股市需要超越不断上升的盈利预期，才能将其创纪录的涨势延续到 2025 年。并非所有投资者都相信他们能做到。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/south-african-stocks-rally-hinges-on-beating-earnings-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 06:22:46 GMT</pubDate>
